The paper deals with object detection, multiple object tracking, and vehicle re-identification, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes an end-to-end network and uses multi-loss training, which are common techniques in deep learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper uses a video dataset and deals with tracking, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO).
